          <div class="cp-acc-body">Works with iPhone 12, 13, 14, 15, and 16 series (all models including Pro and Pro Max) when used with a MagSafe-compatible case.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="cp-acc-item">
          <button class="cp-acc-hd" onclick="cpToggleAcc(this)" type="button">Shipping &amp; Returns <span class="cp-acc-ico">+</span></button>
          <div class="cp-acc-body">Orders processed and shipped within 1–3 business days. Free shipping on orders over $25. Cash on delivery available. 30-day no-questions-asked returns.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

